name: Tezos Tale #03 - Slippery Slope, Acclaimed Alleyway
description: This is a one time street, ya hear? You don't come back here because you know if you come back you ain't ever leaving. It's that captivating of a place; one time is the way to go, unless you wanna live in a slum with a hookah lounge under it for the rest of your life.
